{"share":"38","time":"2012-12-03 18:58:14:000","text":"<p>&nbsp;<\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;\"><strong>1.路人甲<\/strong>：你猜猜我现在在想什么？<\/span><\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\">答：我怎么会知道你在想什么&hellip;&hellip;<\/span><\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\">路人甲：诶？你不是学心理的吗？<\/span><\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\">答：?!@#$*)&amp;*^#@....<img class=\"mceItem emotion\" src=\"http:\/\/s.xnimg.cn\/\/imgpro\/emotions\/ali\/11.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"好囧\"><\/span><\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\"><strong>2.路人乙<\/strong>：你们会占星吗？<\/span><\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\">答：?&gt;@#$($*@#)<img class=\"mceItem emotion\" src=\"http:\/\/s.xnimg.cn\/\/imgpro\/emotions\/ali\/36.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"疑问\"><\/span><\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\"><strong>3.路人丙<\/strong>：噢？心理系啊！那，你给我分析分析？我跟你说哦，前段时间！!$(*&amp;*()$#省略万言书<img class=\"mceItem emotion\" src=\"http:\/\/s.xnimg.cn\/\/imgpro\/emotions\/ali\/40.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"转圈哭\"><\/span><\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\">         <br>    <\/span><\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\"><strong>4.老大爷<\/strong>问：姑娘你学什么？<\/span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\">答：学心理的。 老大爷意味深长地沉吟一声：来姑娘，帮咱家闺女看看手相。 答：?!@#%!*$#!&amp;...<img class=\"mceItem emotion\" src=\"http:\/\/s.xnimg.cn\/\/imgpro\/emotions\/ali\/39.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"抓狂\"><\/span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;\"><strong>5<\/strong>.诶，心理学学什么的？<\/span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;\"> 说来话长&hellip;&hellip;<\/span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;\">心理学研究靠谱吗？<\/span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;\"> 看情况&hellip;&hellip;<\/span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;\">第一印象有那么重要吗？<\/span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;\"> 实验说：￥)@#(*%$）&amp;@#！<\/span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;\">心理学为什么会研究腐女？<\/span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;\"> 因为心理学研究人&hellip;&hellip;<\/span><\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;\"><img class=\"mceItem emotion\" src=\"http:\/\/s.xnimg.cn\/\/imgpro\/emotions\/ali\/49.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"大惊\">你们到底是干什么的！<\/span><\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p><p>于是乎&hellip;&hellip;<\/p><p>    <strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 18.0pt;color: rgb(255,153,0);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);\">邀请诸位非心理系专业的童鞋来聊聊你们眼中的心理学。还你们一个真实的心理学。<\/span><\/strong><\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\">形式：2-4人casual discussion<\/span><\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\">时间：12月4日到12月6日<\/span><\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 12月10日12月16日<\/span><\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 任意一晚，时长约半小时<\/span><\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\">地点：某cafe(短信具体通知) <\/span>&nbsp;<\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\">短信发送或人人留言：<\/span><\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 姓名+院系+手机号+12月X日XX点-XX点 <\/span><\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 到18800119328（孙卉）或人人留言~<img class=\"mceItem emotion\" src=\"http:\/\/s.xnimg.cn\/\/imgpro\/emotions\/ali\/1.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"啊啊啊\"> <\/span><\/p><p>    <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;\"><img thumbnail=\"http:\/\/fmn.rrimg.com\/fmn058\/20121203\/1845\/large_14vv_320c0000b15c118f.jpg\" title=\"photo-media\" src=\"http:\/\/fmn.rrimg.com\/fmn058\/20121203\/1845\/large_14vv_320c0000b15c118f.jpg\" border=\"0\"><\/span><\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p>","title":"今晚我们聊聊心理学","view":"493","textlength":"3663","comment":"88","access":"0","type":"0"}
